title: T206 set – how do I register it?
author: FFIMARRIOTT

posts.post_title: T206 set – how do I register it?
posts.post_content:
Does anyone know how I go about registering a T206 set (520 cards)?
Thanks!!
- Michael

One possibility is, if a psa member with cards that are all psa graded do so psacard.com and it accepts photos of each if you’d like.  I use this site to keep track and register mine, T206insider.com it’s well put together easy to navigate and free of charge.
